{"tid":2025485,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金管局將研究轉數快會否納入其他貨幣！","createTime":"2020-05-20T09:21:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T11:22:35.000Z","uid":63113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"6984307a67c8e7d1987e3c30e108816fc05941a0","tid":2025485,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:21:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32b15658de5940142bbe22b1e926ea3dc2dab021","tid":2025485,"uid":63113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"金管局分四階段落實銀行業開放應用程式介面(API)，容許第三方使用金融機構公開的數據，金管局高級助理總裁劉應彬指，首兩階段開放已落實上馬，第一、二階段分別已收到500及300個申請，但第三、四階段涉及機構客戶資料及私隱，會更審慎地研究，冀今年內可出台準則與銀行商討。<br />\n<br />\n金管局助理總裁(金融基建)鮑克運指，轉數快推出目的是以民為本，香港主要以港幣及人民幣交易，會考慮交易是否擴展至其他貨幣及納入更多交易場景，但短期內未見有關需求。<br />\n<br />\n劉應彬又提到，目前有兩間虛擬銀行仍未進行沙盒試業，但強調不會為虛擬銀行開業時間設限期，相比操之過急地開業，銀行穩妥籌備工作較理想，他又相信，疫情總會過去，但金融科技則是金融及銀行的長遠發展，不會受短期因素影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288860&amp;csid=261_368&amp;PageSpeed=noscript\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1288860%26csid%3D261_368%26PageSpeed%3Dnoscript&d=74ULG85bswSWcCYhLq3krMlSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=87b5337c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1288860&amp;csid=261_368&amp;PageSpeed=noscript</a>"},{"pid":"3b655200e244745890ff02f4a3caf5a6b0796e47","tid":2025485,"uid":18477,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:25:59.000Z","msg":"即係加埋冥通銀行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"669abb672257ce0635ff9459971429662448354e","tid":2025485,"uid":14918,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T09:27:06.000Z","msg":"黃店用FPS美金流通<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a3ae443de82dd360db8e5c22279a90f2d02a9b","tid":2025485,"uid":8050